Use this code to only allow digits and decimal in price field, without $. So they can enter 49, 49.99, 49.00, but not 49.0 or $49
if ( req.body.price ) {
    req.assert('price', 'Enter a price (numbers only)').regex(/^\d+(\.\d{2})?$/);
}